                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170219-81-off449 t18170219-81-cd450"></join>, twenty yards of flannel, value, 15s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18170219-81-victim711" type="victimName">
                     William 
